g  and  mr spelman was a vice president in the alternative investments group at refco where he developed policies procedures and technology for market risk management of derivatives trading portfolios and oversaw allocations to a suite of commodity trading advisors from  to  mr spelman was an associate and risk management analyst for the quantitative equities group at goldman sachs where he was responsible for monitoring the investment risk budgeting process and ensuring consistent portfolio construction across client accounts he covered multiple strategies including index tracking products equity market neutral and the equity components of gtaa portfolios mr spelman began his career in alternative investments as a research analyst at salomon smith barney managed futures trading and earlier as a statistician at arnhold  s bleichroeder advisers mr spelman has been involved in money management since  and holds a ba in asian studies from hobart college “the caliber of professional talent at optima makes us confident we will continue delivering premier alternative investment solutions we have a truly remarkable team” geoffrey lewis managing director and cfo   optima fund ltd top holdings whalewisdom search all search f filers only search sec filer search stocks only search mgmt inv cos only etfs only search active optima fund ltd • hamilton d • hedge fund how do i update this listing optima fund ltd is based out of hamilton the firm last filed a form d notice of exempt offering of securities on  the filing was for a pooled investment fund hedge fund the notice included securities offered of pooled investment fund interests summary dg insider form  form d  create email alert × email notification log in or signup to see more advanced email alert options such as selecting any type of sec form multiple filers or classes of filers and much more or to simply have an email sent to you whenever we receive a new f filing from optima fund ltd enter your email address below and ch